&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Insider is hiring an Account Director (Digital Ad Sales) to join our Financial Services vertical to continue building out the client base and deliver custom solutions.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;Business Insider is for people who are driven, optimistic and always looking forward. Our mission is to inspire action through thought-provoking stories. We tell our audience what they want and need to know to improve their lives and the world with storytelling that is accessible, smart, sometimes unexpected, and always helpful. Our team members embody and uphold Business Insider’s three core values: we are all one team, we are effective, and we get better every day.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role &amp;amp; Team:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;We are looking for experienced, client facing, enthusiastic digital media experts with a proven record of building and nurturing client relationships and partnerships.&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;The FINCO Team works with clients and agencies across the financial sector vertical from banks, credit cards, asset managers, insurance, fintech, payments and crypto. As an Account Director, you will be responsible for a national list of both established and new clients. Successful candidates will be creative thinkers who have exceptional interpersonal skills and are capable of developing relationships through high activity motions, opening new sales pipeline, and closing business from Financial clients.&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;This role reports directly to the VP of Finance Vertical Sales. Candidates &lt;strong&gt;must be willing to travel. &lt;/strong&gt;This position is based in our New York City HQ with an in-office presence of at least 3 days per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;ul1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;Serving as an “evangelist” for Business Insider internally and externally; clearly articulating the company’s unique value proposition in the context of a fragmented research marketplace&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;Lead high-level relationships with key Financial clients and agencies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;Have 5-10, in-depth in-person and virtual meetings (exploratory, presentations, entertainment) with prospective clients and their agencies&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;Develop custom client solutions utilizing Business Insider’s entire suite of products including Branded Content, Display, Video, Social, Programmatic, Data and Live/Virtual Events.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;Develop, maintain, and sustain relationships with media agencies, creative agencies, and clients directly while hitting quarterly sales targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;Work across multiple client and agency partners, i.e. branded content, video, digital and innovation teams, to deliver successful campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;Coordinate effectively with Marketing, Client Services, Media Planning and Studios Teams to create successful ad campaigns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;Focus on brand sell, educating and inspiring our Financial clients to use Business Insider. to enhance their business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;Develop strategic account plans to achieve target revenue goals; hit or exceed these revenue goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;Represent Business Insider at events and serve as a brand ambassador&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Insider is hiring an &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Account Director, Programmatic Sales&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;to join our &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Programmatic Sales Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; to&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;drive our premium programmatic business, expand our first party data offerings and strengthen our relationships with programmatic decision makers&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
