&lt;p&gt;Our Programmatic Sales Team is one of most collaborative groups at Business Insider, working closely with cross-functional teams to deliver data-driven, high-impact solutions that align with our clients&#39; goals and drive measurable results. In addition to internal collaboration with the Direct Sales team and Ad Operations teams, we work with many external partners (DSPs, SSPs) to maintain strong relationships.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
