&lt;p&gt;The Account Director, Programmatic Sales should be a highly motivated and results-driven professional with deep subject matter expertise. This position serves as a key liaison, bridging communication and collaboration both externally and internally. Externally, the role represents Business Insider in building and maintaining strong client relationships. Internally, it acts as a connector between the Direct Sales team and Ad Operations, ensuring seamless coordination, alignment, and execution across departments.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
