&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute a strategic plan to secure new programmatic deals in collaboration with the direct sales team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with the ad operations team to identify and grow existing programmatic accounts through effective relationship-building and optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Client Relationships:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and maintain strong relationships with existing named accounts, understanding their broader advertising goals and identifying opportunities for programmatic campaigns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the Direct Sales team to engage with new clients, understanding their business needs and providing tailored programmatic advertising solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
