&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Insider is hiring a Lifecycle Marketing Manager to join our Growth Marketing team. This role will focus on driving engagement, conversions, and retention among our core audience - transforming casual readers into loyal subscribers.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
