&lt;p&gt;Business Insider’s Singapore bureau is hiring a senior business reporter passionate about technology and AI, with a strong instinct for identifying what matters to our readers in a fast-moving news cycle.&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;This is a full-time role based in Singapore.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
