&lt;li&gt;Identify sharp angles on tech and AI news&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cover fast-moving developments with speed, clarity, and accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Report through interviews with analysts, insiders, and sources&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has the opportunity to produce occasional longer features (700–1,200 words)&lt;/li&gt;
